	<div style="text-align:right;">
		BENDNARTCZUK, Priscila de Souza<sup>1</sup>; LIMA, Nery Nishimura de<sup>2</sup>; BOGISCH, Maria Inês Pinto<sup>3</sup>; NOVAK, Bruna Cristine<sup>4</sup>; MARREIRO, Jessica Caroline<sup>5</sup>; LUCYSZYN, Neoli<sup>6</sup>		<BR>
